        <p>Accessibility is essential for creating an inclusive web experience that accommodates users with various disabilities such as visual, hearing, motor or cognitive impairments. Making your website accessible means that everyone can access and use your website regardless of their physical, sensory, or cognitive abilities.
        <p>
            
        <p>
